26:03.520 --> 26:07.520
Look, my family comes from the region.

26:07.520 --> 26:14.520
Almost 100% of my ancestors came from Poland, Russia, Ukraine and Latvia.

26:15.520 --> 26:20.520
I'm very hesitant to talk in Western media about the realities of the region

26:20.520 --> 26:26.520
because I don't think that Americans have been prepared for quite what the pressures are in this area

26:26.520 --> 26:32.520
and it is incredibly important that we understand just how dangerous this region is,

26:32.520 --> 26:34.520
in part because of the skill level of the players.

26:34.520 --> 26:40.520
Vladimir Putin may be a brute, a butcher, but he's also incredibly skilled.

26:40.520 --> 26:47.520
You have to remember that America's nuclear power effectively came from a bunch of emigres from places like Lvov,

26:47.520 --> 26:53.520
which is now called Lviv, which I think it was a Polish city, which is now claimed to be Ukrainian.

26:53.520 --> 27:01.520
We have to appreciate that this is a region that is incredibly skilled, incredibly dangerous,

27:01.520 --> 27:08.520
a source of intellectual horsepower which built America's own atomic arsenal, refugees from the area.

27:08.520 --> 27:13.520
So I think that you just have to understand that most of us are way out of our depths

27:13.520 --> 27:20.520
if we don't have great information, we don't have cultural and historical understanding of the tensions between these people.

27:20.520 --> 27:24.520
I want to just change tack to free speech.

27:24.520 --> 27:29.520
