35:16.520 --> 35:23.520
because presumably this is all about statecraft and the extremely secret programs as to why are we in Wuhan,

35:24.520 --> 35:29.520
talking about inserting, if you're in Cleveland sites and humanizing coronavirus,

35:30.520 --> 35:38.520
it's an absolutely terrifying vacuum of knowledge, and I don't think we know why.

35:38.520 --> 35:46.520
I think that this, very likely, we're trying to play 12-dimensional chess and we're barely able to play checkers,

35:46.520 --> 35:52.520
and this goes back to the original point about, I think it was April of 1953 when we figured out DNA,

35:52.520 --> 35:56.520
and then 10 years later we had the genetic code with the work of Marshall Nirenberg.

35:56.520 --> 36:03.520
It's so much power, and the treaties that we've signed are possibly nonsensical.

36:03.520 --> 36:07.520
I mean, we have a problem that we don't develop offensive weapons,

36:07.520 --> 36:12.520
but defensive measures can be easily converted to offensive measures.

36:12.520 --> 36:18.520
We have put restrictions on ourselves that we then attempt to get out of.

36:18.520 --> 36:25.520
Almost certainly this has to do with questions that we don't want resolved in public,

36:25.520 --> 36:29.520
and I came from, you know, I'm an old man now.

36:29.520 --> 36:37.520
At 58, I remember the church hearings, the pike hearings, the Watergate hearings, the Iran-Contra hearings.

36:37.520 --> 36:45.520
