Effectively, that you're looking at something that's extraordinarily simple,

42:24.520 --> 42:28.520
that Einstein's theory, if you will, began with four degrees of freedom,

42:28.520 --> 42:31.520
which you can think of as any four degrees of freedom,

42:31.520 --> 42:34.520
like treble, mid, bass, and reverb on an amp.

42:34.520 --> 42:38.520
Then what he did was he took the four degrees of freedom,

42:38.520 --> 42:43.520
and he said, let's put three rulers and one watch as measuring devices

42:43.520 --> 42:49.520
and six protractors to measure the angles between all of those four objects.

42:49.520 --> 42:52.520
