43:10.520 --> 43:14.520
Imagine that that record was, in some sense, 14-dimensional data.

43:14.520 --> 43:18.520
The stylus was Einstein's spacetime metric,

43:18.520 --> 43:22.520
and the gramophone is the four-dimensional world that you perceive.

43:22.520 --> 43:25.520
